product.title: Kawaii Cat Sushi Harajuku Cotton Unisex Tee | NEW
product.body_html:
• Description
    • FAQ
    • Shipping

    • Spreading smiles and joy wherever you go

      Introducing our adorable and trendy Kawaii Cat and Sushi-themed Cotton Tee - a joyous fusion of cuteness and Japanese pop culture. This charming tee showcases not one, but six irresistibly cute cats and sushi printed on the front.

      Whether you're a fan of kawaii culture, a sushi enthusiast, or simply love unique and eye-catching fashion, this loose tee is a must-have addition to your collection.

      Available in 13 colors and 6 different sizes, measurements are shown below.       We always recommend choosing 1-2 sizes larger and comparing the measurements in the sizing chart to a tee that fits you.


      Size (inches) S M L XL XXL XXXL
      Bust 36 38 41 43 44 47
      Length (inches) 26 27 28 29 30 30
                   
      Size (cm) S M L XL XXL XXXL
      Bust 92 98 104 110 114 120
      Length      (cm) 67 70 72 74 76 78

      If you are interested in more items like this, please check out our website www.kawaiies.com


      Features

      ✨ 100% Cotton 
      ✨ Short sleeve tees
      ✨ Designs printed on the front
      ✨ Japanese Sushi and Cats


      Measurements may be off by 1-5cm for rounding up to a whole number.

    • Please follow the washing labels when cleaning the garment:

       Max temperature 30c, or cold water. Reverse the garment to protect the print.

       Do not bleach

       Dry by the sun or hang it to dry. 

       Dry cleaning

       

    • FREE Tracked Shipping to the United States, Canada, United Kingdom, Australia, New Zealand, Germany, Spain, France, Italy, Austria, Netherlands, and many more. Find out more here: Shipping Policy.

      Packaging time: 1-3 Business days

      Shipping time: Est 5-30 Business days
